msgid "Not at all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0002"
msgid "Absolutely!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0003"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Next we're going to add something called a <CLT><CLT 3>Truth\n"
"Flashback<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>If you aim at a weak spot and hold down the\n"
"<CLT><CLT 3>%CTRL_TRIAL_SHOOT%<CLT><CLT 23>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>...then you'll <CLT><CLT 3>memorize<CLT><CLT 23> that weak spot.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>This memorized phrase can only be shot once as a\n"
"single <CLT><CLT 3>Truth Bullet<CLT><CLT 23>.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0008"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>If you shoot or change the Truth Bullet, it will\n"
"disappear from your Truth Cylinder.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0009"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>However, you can use this flashback feature as many\n"
"times as you want.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>If you don't seem to have the answer to a <CLT><CLT 3>lie or\n"
"contradiction<CLT><CLT 23> in your loaded Truth Bullets...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>...it might be wise to memorize a different weak spot\n"
"and use that to make your case.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0012"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>When's the best time to flashback? Well, you'll just\n"
"have to use your keen wits, won't you?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0013"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>In this case, though, I will say that if you don't use\n"
"a flashback, you won't be refuting anything.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>Well then...good luck, and have fun!\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"<CLT 23>A <CLT><CLT 3>new element has been added<CLT><CLT 23> to Nonstop Debates.\n"
"Would you like to hear more?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
